item.title: 614 Client wont start?

item.description:

[quote=“Kidpaparoach, post:3, topic:398279”]Their MAY be a anti-leach. If you can’t find it try searching(ctrl + f) ‘ip’ or ‘server’ untill you find like something that has a bracket which looks like it needs a value put in. If not try a different client with it, also check the ports on the server and client are the same i.e. i’ve changed mines to 5555 just search 43594 (most commonly used) is both the source and client.

Hope this helped :)[/quote]
